\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4794022 HR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5065330\charrsid15021746 No. Hadn\rquote t got a vote then.
